*************WARNING!**************

This small shout box is not proteceted against SQL injection, so before using make sure you real escape string or use any other method of protection against this hack!

***********************************

HOW TO USE

- To use on you'r web, just include the shout box php file ( include_once(shout_box.php) ), and then style it and position it with some css (id="shout_box"). 
- Put the class_lib.php in the same folder as the shout_box.php file, or modify the paths acordingly.
- Use shout_box_table.sql to create database table
- Follow the comments...

LICENCE

None! Use it as you see fit!



